accesscontrol-info: This message described that the current page your on is protected.
accesscontrol-info-box: This message describes that your current mediawiki uses the AccessControl extension to allow restrict access to the site.
accesscontrol-wrong-group-title:
An error message shown when user provided a group name that cannot be uses as a title.

Parameters:
* the group name
accesscontrol-group-does-not-exist:
An error message shown when non-existing title used as a group parameter inside the the <accesscontrol> tag.

Parameters:
* the provided title
